      "widgets_values": [
        "CharacterPose custom nodes workflow (txt2img variant)\n\nFor IDENTITY-PRESERVING pose transfer, prefer:\n  workflows/pose_transfer_warp.json\n(warp real pixels + img2img repair — same orientation only).\n\nModels:\nIf ComfyUI reports Missing Models on open, use Missing Models / Download.\nFolders: models/checkpoints, models/controlnet, models/clip_vision, models/ipadapter.\n\nSetup:\n1. Install this package into ComfyUI/custom_nodes/_ComfyUI_CharacterPose\n2. Install via Manager: comfyui_controlnet_aux, ComfyUI_IPAdapter_plus\n3. Download any missing models from the Missing Models dialog\n\nOrientation: warp cannot invent front/back from a side sprite. Use idle_side / walk_side_* with side-facing sources. Multi-view = Flux Kontext (future)."
